Package: linux-universal-app-installer
Version: 2.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Linux Universal App Installer Team <installer@example.com>
Installed-Size: 151
Depends: python3-pyqt5 (>= 5.15.0), python3 (>= 3.8), python3-setuptools
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/linux-app-installer/linux-universal-app-installer
Description: Professional drag-and-drop application installer for Linux
 A comprehensive application installer that supports multiple package formats
 including .deb, .appimage, .tar.gz, .snap, and .flatpak files. Features a
 modern GUI with drag-and-drop functionality, batch installation, and
 professional desktop integration similar to Windows installers.
